  "title": "fix(configure): ignore invalid userToken",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for submitting a pull request!\r\n  Please provide enough information so that others can review your pull request.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR fixes `configure` widget to ignore invalid userToken.\r\n\r\nAlthough we have fixed nullish user token issues in `insights` middleware, if users still put `null` into `configure` widget, it was passing the `null` as a string to search api. We ignore it from now on.",
